snippet.title: BEST DRUGSTORE CONCEALER UNDER P500 (Philippines) | Denise Botor
snippet.description:
#LorealInfallibleConcealer
Hi everyone! I am so happy I found the best, budget friendly and full coverage concealer from the drugstore. Yes, from the drugstore!

Products Mentioned:
Loreal Infallible Full wear Concealer (My shade - Almond) - https://shp.ee/fcu69yx


This is a review on the Loreal Infallible Full wear Concealer. I also did a side by side comparison of the Loreal and the OG Nars Radiant creamy concealer.  I hope you guys enjoy this video! 

IG: @denisebotor
